{"tid":2086113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨安法係可以有追溯期！","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T17:07:34.000Z","uid":6777,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"07d584818d95f5c6d554bdd5b15c804824f1c1e7","tid":2086113,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"搞清楚幾樣野<br />\n法律原則同埋實際操作<br />\n<br />\n因為新法律係無追溯期<br />\n但釋法係可以有追溯期<br />\n<br />\n代表咩？假設今日佢話黨安法無追溯期<br />\n<br />\n但因為你係未有黨安法前，已經違反左基本法23條<br />\n<br />\n因為黨安法係設定左關於違反 23條既罰則<br />\n<br />\n所以依然可以透過釋法去追溯番處理違反23條既情況<br />\n<br />\n共產黨有咩做唔出？笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e139a697a523cb1a491b67c9fbe1106c0fd46cf","tid":2086113,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01a2b93191709bb7cfc3b5e147f85ff9bf8d03c1","tid":2086113,"uid":67065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"照你邏輯黎講<br />\n佢國安法同23條係兩樣野黎<br />\n如果好似你咁講都要立左23條<br />\n未立法要釋法 應該只可以釋立左既法"},{"pid":"9f757ec50d5837c963d0c0ced7e46660f224f8be","tid":2086113,"uid":6777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01a2b93191709bb7cfc3b5e147f85ff9bf8d03c1","tid":2086113,"uid":67065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"照你邏輯黎講<br />\n佢國安法同23條係兩樣野黎<br />\n如果好似你咁講都要立左23條<br />\n未立法要釋法 應該只可以釋立左既法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"23條本身已經係已有既憲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂立法只係立本地法律<br />\n<br />\n佢可以釋法去解讀 23條<br />\n講到不嬲所有相關情況都係違法，只係之前無罰則<br />\n<br />\n而家有，所以全部都有效"},{"pid":"b89e0843e250f2eba6243637d5729ecfa1bd63cd","tid":2086113,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b4761eb0e7b427e600b3365c01e3fbc8279e1","tid":2086113,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"唸多左"},{"pid":"cafb14b3b3dd3e816efb0afacbf70fa10c281f72","tid":2086113,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f91b4761eb0e7b427e600b3365c01e3fbc8279e1","tid":2086113,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"唸多左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"咁信共產黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa58666d0d16f661ea39f4a80f5e857e108c293","tid":2086113,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"驚閪<br />\n拉鳩我去打靶吖笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606deebc63c4c36ea20e3dd9e42af8c94c9d9b17","tid":2086113,"uid":350688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"根本無需要咁複雜<br />\n共產黨聽日就話你強姦左隻豬<br />\n對國家主席不心存驚畏都可以告得你入<br />\n有冇追溯期一直都唔重要"},{"pid":"a6bd7d06a54ffe8fd75456bb47287e6971acb407",